            <title>[DERBY-2242] Convert jdbcapi/metadata.java to JUnit test.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2242</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create a test for DatabaseMetaData that matches the testing of metadata.java.&lt;br/&gt;
Should also handle the odbc_metadata variant.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Once created can be used by other tests to ensure database meta data works in other situations, such as upgrade and read-only databases.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
